@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@token = cole_o_token_aqui

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/healthz

### Swagger
GET {{baseUrl}}/swagger/v1/swagger.json

### Scalar/OpenAPI
GET {{baseUrl}}/openapi/v1.json

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users/authenticate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "gmarcone@gmail.com",
  "senha": "Senha@123"
}

### CBHPM
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cbhpm?page=1&pageSize=10&procedimento=consulta
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Pacientes
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/pacientes?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Licenca atual
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/licencas/current
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Agenda
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events?from=2026-06-01T00:00:00.000Z&to=2026-06-30T23:59:59.000Z
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Criar evento
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Consulta de acompanhamento",
  "description": "Retorno com paciente",
  "start": "2026-06-15T13:00:00.000Z",
  "end": "2026-06-15T14:00:00.000Z",
  "notifyMedicalProfile": true,
  "notifyUser": true,
  "reminderPeriodMinutes": 60
}
